Name: Fizik
About the game: Fizik is a first-person parkour game that can be either relaxing or challenging depending on the simulation you decide to play. Master the timing of your jumps, wall-runs and grapples to beat your personal best runs. 3 types of levels. Green levels are low-pressure: you can explore the space and take your time to master the parkour skills. Red levels are intense: they require precision movement and quick reflexes to maneuver through. Bonus challenge levels are unlocked by collecting secret orbs! Key Features: Wall-run like a badass Chain Grapples together to glide through the levels Slide down rediculous slopes to build momentum Graciously bounce between bounce pads 70+ Exciting Levels with secret collectables! 10 secret levels!
